headline: CBRE IM Backs IPUT Real Estate Dublin with Significant Equity Commitment
summary: DUBLIN, February 18, 2026--IPUT Real Estate ('IPUT'), Dublin's leading property investment company, announces it has raised €175 million in new equity from CBRE Investment Management Indirect Strategies ("CBRE IM") to continue to grow its prime Dublin office portfolio.
